{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/markdown-syntax/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"简介\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B\" aria-label=\"简介 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>简介</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Markdown\">Markdown</a>是一种为了提高文档易读性与易写性的纯文本格式规范，其可以转换成HTML，从而可以利用CSS定制其样式。Markdown语法非常简单，而且语法符号也是为了快速书写文本而设计。Markdown发布已经很久了，其初由John Gruber与Aaron Swartz于2004年合作发布，<a href=\"https://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/basics\">最初的发布版本</a>。直到现在，并没有一个统一的标准规范，各个实现版本会有些不同，不过基础的语法基本是相同的。Markdown已经应用在很多地方，如Github、Stackoverflow、reddit等网站，也应用于项目的ReadMe文件、一些论坛、写邮件、博客等地方。有多种实现的语言版本，也有多个系统平台上的编辑器实现，在线编辑器也有，这些可以谷歌会得到很多结果。</p>\n<h2 id=\"语法\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95\" aria-label=\"语法 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>语法</h2>\n<h3 id=\"标题\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98\" aria-label=\"标题 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>标题</h3>\n<p>标题是以<code class=\"language-text\">#</code>开头的文本，如<code class=\"language-text\">#标题</code>，一级标题是一个<code class=\"language-text\">#</code>号，二级两个，直到六级，分别对应HTML当中的<code class=\"language-text\">h1~h6</code>标签。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">#一级标题\n##二级标题\n###三级标题\n…\n######六级标题</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"段落\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%AE%B5%E8%90%BD\" aria-label=\"段落 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>段落</h3>\n<p>段落就是普通的文本，空行表示换一个段落。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">这是段落一这是段落一\n这还是段落一\n\n这是段落二</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"引用\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"引用 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>引用</h3>\n<p>引用是以<code class=\"language-text\">&gt;</code>开头的文本。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&gt; 这是一段引用这是一段引用\n&gt; 这和上面是同一段引用\n&gt; 这和上面是同一段引用</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"代码\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81\" aria-label=\"代码 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>代码</h3>\n<p>内嵌代码用反引号<code class=\"language-text\">`</code>，如<code class=\"language-text\">`background: #fff;`</code>。代码块使用四个空格或一个Tab缩进。</p>\n<h3 id=\"列表\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" aria-label=\"列表 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>列表</h3>\n<p>无序列表用<code class=\"language-text\">*</code>或<code class=\"language-text\">+</code>或<code class=\"language-text\">-</code>开头表示：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">* 项目一\n* 项目二\n* 项目三</code></pre></div>\n<p>或</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">+ 项目一\n+ 项目二\n+ 项目三</code></pre></div>\n<p>或</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">- 项目一\n- 项目二\n- 项目三</code></pre></div>\n<p>有序列表用数字跟一个英文句点表示：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">1. 项目一\n2. 项目二\n3. 项目三</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"强调\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%BC%BA%E8%B0%83\" aria-label=\"强调 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>强调</h3>\n<p>包括斜体与粗体，分别对应HTML中的<code class=\"language-text\">em</code>与<code class=\"language-text\">strong</code>标签。斜体为两边各一个<code class=\"language-text\">#</code>或<code class=\"language-text\">_</code>包裹，而粗体用<code class=\"language-text\">##</code>或<code class=\"language-text\">__</code>包裹，斜体可与粗体嵌套，比如：<code class=\"language-text\">##_斜粗体_##</code>。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">#斜体#\n_斜体_\n##粗体##\n__粗体__\n##_斜粗体_##`</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"超链接\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%B6%85%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5\" aria-label=\"超链接 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>超链接</h3>\n<p>超链接文本放在<code class=\"language-text\">[]</code>中，而超链接地址放在紧跟其后面的<code class=\"language-text\">()</code>中。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">[百度](http://www.baidu.com)</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"图片\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87\" aria-label=\"图片 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>图片</h3>\n<p>图片与超链接语法类似：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>一个英文感叹号<code class=\"language-text\">!</code></li>\n<li>接一个[]包裹的文本，其文本为图片无法显示时的替代文字，<code class=\"language-text\">![替代文字]</code></li>\n<li>接一个()包裹的图片链接，<code class=\"language-text\">![替代文字](http://www.domain.com/photo.jpg)</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>在图片链接的后面还可以跟一个鼠标悬停在图片上时显示的文字：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">![替代文字](http://www.domain.com/photo.jpg &quot;鼠标悬停显示的文字&quot;)</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"转义特殊字符\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%BD%AC%E4%B9%89%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6\" aria-label=\"转义特殊字符 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>转义特殊字符</h3>\n<p>Markdown允许通过反斜杠<code class=\"language-text\">\\</code>来转义下面的特殊字符：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">\\   反斜杠\n`   反引号\n*   星号\n_   下划线\n{}  花括号\n[]  方括号\n()  括号\n#   井号\n+   加号\n-   减号\n.   英文句点\n!   感叹号</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"更好的参考：\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%9B%B4%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%EF%BC%9A\" aria-label=\"更好的参考： permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>更好的参考：</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Markdown Here Cheatsheet: <a href=\"https://github.com/adam-p/markdown-here/wiki/Markdown-Here-Cheatsheet\">https://github.com/adam-p/markdown-here/wiki/Markdown-Here-Cheatsheet</a></li>\n<li>Markdown语法说明：<a href=\"http://wowubuntu.com/markdown/\">http://wowubuntu.com/markdown/</a></li>\n<li>Github Markdown Basics: <a href=\"https://help.github.com/articles/markdown-basics\">https://help.github.com/articles/markdown-basics</a></li>\n<li>What is Markdown: <a href=\"http://whatismarkdown.com/\">http://whatismarkdown.com/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"在线编辑器\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9C%A8%E7%BA%BF%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8\" aria-label=\"在线编辑器 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>在线编辑器</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Cmd Markdown编辑阅读器：<a href=\"https://www.zybuluo.com/mdeditor\">https://www.zybuluo.com/mdeditor</a></li>\n<li>Dillinger Online Markdown Editor: <a href=\"http://dillinger.io/\">http://dillinger.io/</a></li>\n</ul>","timeToRead":4,"excerpt":"简介 Markdown是一种为了提高文档易读性与易写性的纯文本格式规范，其可以转换成HTML，从而可以利用CSS定制其样式。Markdown语法非常简单，而且语法符号也是为了快速书写文本而设计。Markdown发布已经很久了，其初由John Gruber与Aaron Swartz…","frontmatter":{"title":"Markdown语法学习","cover":"","date":"2014-04-09","category":"其他","tags":["Markdown","Markdown语法"]},"fields":{"slug":"/markdown-syntax/","date":"2014-04-08T16:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/markdown-syntax/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}